## üê≥ **Docker Support**

```dockerfile
FROM python:3.11-slim

# Install system dependencies
RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
    ffmpeg \
    libopus-dev \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

# Install TgCaller
RUN pip install tgcaller[video]

# Copy your bot
COPY . /app
WORKDIR /app

CMD ["python", "bot.py"]
```

