## üõ†Ô∏è **Development**

### **Setup**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/tgcaller/tgcaller.git
cd tgcaller

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

# Install in development mode
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest tests/ -v
```

